90 Minute result + Over/Under Goals + Anytime Goal Scorer = Spincast

This is a betting tool exclusive to BetVictor. The aim of the SPINCAST is to select the 90 Minute result, Over/Under Total goals and the Anytime Goal Scorer in a particular match. Select the match you want to bet on from the match menu.

For example:
Barcelona to win + Over 2.5 Goals + Messi to Score Anytime = Spincast

Spincast is available on all major leagues
